@startuml
!includeurl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/proveo-ca/identity/refs/heads/main/proveo.iuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor User

package "Docker Container (Harness: Chess Coach)" {
    
    package "Web UI" {
        [SolidJS Chessboard] as SolidJS
    }

    package "Ktor Backend Bridge" {
        [Ktor REST API] as Ktor
    }

    [Bash Orchestrator] as Bash

    package "LLM Sub-Agents (Qwen 2.5)" {
        actor "State Analyzer" as Analyzer
        actor "Strategy Agent" as Strategy
        actor "Dialogue Agent" as Dialogue
    }

    package "Kotlin CLI Tools" {
        [Move Validator] as Validator
        [Engine Bridge] as Bridge
    }

    package "External Binaries" {
        [Stockfish Engine] as Stockfish
    }

    database "State Storage" as State {
        [game_state.fen] as FEN
        [game_history.pgn] as PGN
    }
}

User <---> SolidJS : User Actions / Board render
SolidJS <-> Ktor : HTTP Requests
Ktor ..> Bridge : (If Hint) Request Top 3 Moves
Ktor ..> State : (If History) Read past FEN states

Ktor <--> Bash : Subprocess (bash orchestrator.sh) moves bridge

Bash ---> Analyzer : Triggers Analysis
Analyzer ---> State : Reads State
Analyzer --> Bridge : Requests Evaluation
Bridge --> Stockfish : UCI Protocol
Analyzer -> Strategy : Passes Analysis
Strategy --> Validator : Proposes SAN move
Validator --> Bridge : Checks Legality
Strategy --> Bash : Returns Valid Move

Bash ------> State : Updates State
Bash ----> Dialogue : Requests \nCoaching Commentary
Dialogue .up..> User : Outputs Coaching Advice

User -[hidden]-> SolidJS

@enduml
